description: The best way to turn any day into a tropical vacation, Kona Ice of Wichita Falls is coming right to you! Serving up fantastic shaved ice like no other, Kona Ice is always flavored just how you want it thanks to their unique Flavor Wave station. So if you're looking for the sweetest treat to help you beat the heat, look no further than Kona Ice of Wichita Falls!
name: Kona Ice of Wichita Falls
